{"title":"JDK--centOS安装jdk步骤：","date":"2019-10-31T12:15:52.688Z","link":"2019/10/31/JDK--centOS安装jdk步骤：","updated":"2019-09-27T00:48:40.194Z","content":"<h6 id=\"centOS安装jdk步骤：\">centOS安装jdk步骤：<a href=\"2019/10/31/JDK--centOS安装jdk步骤：#centOS安装jdk步骤：\"></a></h6><p>1.搜索：yum search java|grep jdk</p>\n<p>2.找到你想要的jdk版本后的：yum install java-1.8.0-openjdk</p>\n<p>3.安装好后：cd /usr/lib/jvm 进入jvm ls查看jdk版本</p>\n<p>4.vim /etc/profile在文件末尾加入以下环境变量</p>\n<p>5.加入以下环境配置</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#set java environment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-1.8.0-openjdk-1.8.0.212.b04-0.el7_6.x86_64</span><br><span class=\"line\">JRE_HOME=<span class=\"variable\">$JAVA_HOME</span>/jre</span><br><span class=\"line\">CLASS_PATH=.:<span class=\"variable\">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib/dt.jar:<span class=\"variable\">$JAVA_HOME</span>/lib/tools.jar:<span class=\"variable\">$JRE_HOME</span>/lib</span><br><span class=\"line\">PATH=<span class=\"variable\">$PATH</span>:<span class=\"variable\">$JAVA_HOME</span>/bin:<span class=\"variable\">$JRE_HOME</span>/bin</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">export</span> JAVA_HOME JRE_HOME CLASS_PATH PATH</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>6.java -version查看版本</p>\n<h6 id=\"centOS安装jre\">centOS安装jre:<a href=\"2019/10/31/JDK--centOS安装jdk步骤：#centOS安装jre\"></a></h6><h3 id=\"sadfasf\">sadfasf<a href=\"2019/10/31/JDK--centOS安装jdk步骤：#sadfasf\"></a></h3><h6 id=\"centOS编译并运行java文件：\">centOS编译并运行java文件：<a href=\"2019/10/31/JDK--centOS安装jdk步骤：#centOS编译并运行java文件：\"></a></h6>","prev":{"title":"Docker--centOS安装操作Docker","link":"2019/10/31/Docker--centOS安装操作Docker"},"next":{"title":"CentOS安装使用，远程连接MySql","link":"2019/10/31/CentOS安装使用，远程连接MySql"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/10/31/JDK--centOS安装jdk步骤：/"}